Loving #Python3.5 PEP 448 for overwriting a dictionary of default values:

>>> defaults = {"lenny": "white", "carl": "black"}
>>> overwrite = {"lenny": "yellow"}
>>> new = {**defaults, **overwrite}
>>> new
{'lenny': 'yellow', 'carl': 'black'}

